@startuml
title UC-06 Create Community Post
actor Player
participant "Web Frontend" as Web
participant "Community API" as API
database "Database" as DB

Player -> Web : Submit post
Web -> API : POST /community/posts
API -> API : Validate content and metadata
API -> DB : Insert post
DB -->> API : Saved
API -->> Web : Published post
Web -->> Player : Show post detail
@enduml

